  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Inline CSI volumes that are embedded in Pod specs still trigger all volume operation stages (attach, device mount, mount).  Similar to plugin.CanAttach, a new plugin-wide method should be able to turn device mount off when the source is ephemeral volume.\r\n\r\n**References**\r\nSee volume mount operation : https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/897d62ace79a8fa72f9825e065b2b67fdba65bec/pkg/volume/util/operationexecutor/operation_generator.go#L516\r\n\r\nThis issue will use code from https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/issues/75830",
